A morphological layer for the German part of the SMULTRON corpus. Layer was annotated according to the STTS tagset and the annotation guidelines of the Tiger corpus.
Coordinator: Thomas Müller Annotators: Francesca Caratti, Arne Recknagel
This distribution contains a morphological layer for the SMULTRON corpus [0]. The annotation process is described in :
@InProceedings{mueller2015, author = {M\"uller, Thomas and Sch\"utze, Hinrich}, title = {Robust Morphological Tagging with Word Representations}, booktitle = {Proceedings of NAACL}, year = {2015}, }
[0] http://www.cl.uzh.ch/research/parallelcorpora/paralleltreebanks/smultron_en.html
